rldregora.junglecave.adventurer_diary.title=Adventurer's Diary
rldregora.junglecave.adventurer_diary.author=D'kar Origins
rldregora.junglecave.adventurer_diary.lore=This book contains basic information on biomes.
rldregora.junglecave.adventurer_diary.page.1=#-#-#-#-#-#-#-#-#-#\n     Biome Notes\n#-#-#-#-#-#-#-#-#-#\n\n1. Index\n2. Introduction\n3. Temperate\n4. Hot Moist\n5. Dry Hot\n6. Dry Cold\n7. Oceanic
rldregora.junglecave.adventurer_diary.page.2=§lIntroduction§r\n-------------------\nIf anyone finds this book, I am D'kar Origins and I am a adventurer with a interest for nature's work. Such as the Jotumheim Caves to the south or the mighty mountains to the north east.
rldregora.junglecave.adventurer_diary.page.3=§lTemperate Climate§r\n-------------------\nI started traveling from the southern part of what we call the Highlands and ventured north. Here i saw mountains, rich in resources and ancient structures. Some of which seem to have been made from casted rock.
rldregora.junglecave.adventurer_diary.page.4=§lHot Moist Climate§r\n-------------------\nCurrently, I find myself in the Rainforest, a moist hot climate zone rich in fresh water and a whole different climate zone below the surface that somewhat resembles a swamp.
rldregora.junglecave.adventurer_diary.page.5=§lDry Hot Climate§r\n-------------------\nA most harsh zone with huge strangely shaped rocks that are hollow and strangely stable for their size and shape. This climate is rich when it comes to the Dregorian history but lacks everything else.
rldregora.junglecave.adventurer_diary.page.6=§lCold Dry Climate§r\n-------------------\nCold, Barren... I didn't had much of a chance to explore any further as hordes of corrupted wandered the ice. Perhaps it is best to venture forth and forget about this place.\n\n 
rldregora.junglecave.adventurer_diary.page.7=§lOceanic Climates§r\n-------------------\nI never even dreamt about writing a oceanic climate entry. However to my surprise the oceans have a huge micro climate zone underneath the fast body of water. A whole cave system at that!
